issue.title: Incorrect description in spanish skill
issue.body: Calls for progress in Spanish tomato assistant must be ordered to reverse, in the description of the skill is wrong. The right to work is: "Alexa, pide a ayudante de tomate el progreso"

issue.title: Add support for brazilian portuguese (PT-BR)
issue.body:
Add support for this device work with Brazilian Portuguese language (PT-BR). It's current being tested and released as a Beta Test by Amazon. Only a few people has it enabled at the time, but Amazon will officially release this language very soon.

May I submit a pull request with the code that needed to be implemented in order to support this language?

Thanks for the project!
